{"tid":1976220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"nmslese 搭巴士倒到成地都係珍珠奶茶","createTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T13:21:16.000Z","uid":140956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9506d886130545a73e717df78dd0caa98ae1db","tid":1976220,"uid":140956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"屌你咩 搞到成地黏答答又唔抹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/17/134909_0a4e05d0a5e08d4f56a684f6e30c4c33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2F134909_0a4e05d0a5e08d4f56a684f6e30c4c33.png&h=bcbb3958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68d77575ad61564bf7cde76f432bd507997d935a","tid":1976220,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"屙屎屙尿都有"},{"pid":"5eca565ed9f6e741a8479ff3a89cc2c07c15e05b","tid":1976220,"uid":140956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d77575ad61564bf7cde76f432bd507997d935a","tid":1976220,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"屙屎屙尿都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"睇睇下d珍珠係地下都幾似屎<br />\nSor 如果你飲緊珍奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7f408fe559f3d2843e8a0a2d0935d25ee60743","tid":1976220,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的珍珠奶茶倒瀉了<br />\n事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞<br />\n發現倒瀉了的珍珠奶茶<br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方<br />\n再為其拍照<br />\n<br />\n這短短的三十分鐘<br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間<br />\n倒瀉了的珍珠奶茶<br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西<br />\n而那膠杯著地的那一聲<br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音<br />\n<br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情<br />\n也未必是最糟<br />\n因為最糟的<br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現<br />\n又或者根本就是自己<br />\n我想我找到了答案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e6ec89034665d29224697b2a037664a898da7","tid":1976220,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個清潔姐姐多得佢唔少"}]}